'''''Narâg''''' is a [[Khuzdul]] word derived from the root NRG ("black"), stated at one point to the possible origin of the river-name ''[[Narog]]''.<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 37</ref>

==Example==
*''[[Narag-zâram|'''Narag'''-zâram]]'' = "Black Lake"
